28. Race Conditions
Race condition occurs when multiple threads modify shared data simultaneously, causing unpredictable results.
Solution:
•	Locks (threading.Lock)
•	Semaphores
•	Atomic operations
Interview insight:
👉 Always protect shared resources in concurrent systems.
